Saints Peter And Paul Parish

Eternal Flame Faith Formation

Welcome to the new faith formation program for St. Bernadette, St. John the Baptist, Nativity of
 our Lord, St. Mary and SS Peter and Paul churches. You will be regsitering every child for a
 once a month family session and for a student child session (2 times per month in person or
 homestudy).

*Required fields

select 2 clsses per child Each child should be registered for 1 family session per month AND 1 choice of child session. Confirmation students do not need to have a family session. They will be required to choose the "Confirmation - no family session needed" as their second session.
That child session can be a different day/time than the family session. (for example Family session at 6:00pm Mondays and child sesion grade 4 at 3:45 Monday)
The child's session choice is for 2 in person classes per month or may choose homestudy in addition to the family session.
All families, including home study, are expected to attend at least 6 of the 7 planned family sessions this year. To avoid an absence, you can switch to a different session if a conflict arises by emailing us so we have materials prepared.
